show working directory at prompt: PS1="\w $ "

Convert Personal Information Store (PL1 etc) SSL file to .key and .crt files , from shell:

openssl pkcs12 -in path.p12 -out newfile.key.pem -nocerts -nodes -passin 'pass:xxx'
openssl pkcs12 -in path.p12 -out newfile.crt.pem -clcerts -nokeys -passin 'pass:xxx'
